# Feicai Product Manager - TRAE Rules Configuration
# Version: 1.0.0
# Updated: 2026-04-29

## Keyword Triggers

When user input matches these keywords, activate Feicai Product Manager:

### Primary Keywords
- "feicai" → Activate Feicai PM Agent
- "废材" → Activate Feicai PM Agent
- "废才" → Activate Feicai PM Agent

### Command Keywords
- "boss模式" → Activate Boss Mode (full automation)
- "产品4.0" → Activate with Product Spec v4.0
- "chanpin4.0" → Activate with Product Spec v4.0

### Shortcuts
- "/feicai" → Quick activation
- "/boss" → Boss mode activation
- "/pm" → Product manager mode

## Agent Configuration

### Main Agent: feicai-product-manager
- Mode: agent
- Temperature: 0.3
- Color: #3b82f6 (Blue)

### Available Sub-Agents
1. product-manager-demand - Demand collection
2. design-brief-builder - Design brief
3. design-maker - Design creation
4. dev-planner - Development planning
5. dev-builder - Development execution
6. code-reviewer - Code review
7. bug-fixer - Bug fixing
8. release-builder - Release & deploy
9. feedback-writer - Feedback recording
10. evolution-engine - Evolution engine
11. skill-builder - Skill creation

## Workflow Activation

### On Keyword Match:
1. Load Feicai PM Agent definition
2. Initialize with user context
3. Execute appropriate workflow based on keywords

### Workflow Priority:
1. "boss模式" → Full automation workflow
2. "产品4.0" / "chanpin4.0" → Product Spec v4.0 workflow
3. Other keywords → Standard demand collection

## Custom Instructions

When Feicai keywords are detected:
- Set agent role to "废才产品经理"
- Activate product development workflow
- Follow CLAUDE.md principles
- Enable all available skills

## File Locations

- Agent definitions: ~/.trae/agents/
- Rules config: ~/.trae/rules/feicai.rules
- Skills: ~/.trae/skills/

